<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shén jiāng zhì huì gěi wǒ 迦南743</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhì huì zhì huì, shén jiāng zhì huì gěi wǒ.
 jì qiǎo jì qiǎo, shén jiāng jì qiǎo gěi wǒ.
 dài lǐng dài lǐng, dài lǐng bǎi xìng jìng bài.
 róng yào róng yào, róng yào chōng mǎn shèng diàn.</lyrics>
